{"tid":800643,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日等巴士都要比對夫婦屌...","createTime":"2018-08-31T04:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T17:38:36.000Z","uid":29476,"like":3622,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"91720d1b899a0a4207340d7f2d76515f56b6945d","tid":800643,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T04:48:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說琴日等巴士翻屋企<br />\n左手攞住一袋野 右手攞住包檸檬茶<br />\n戴住耳機一路聽歌一路行一路走<br />\n去到巴士站 見後面有大概心口咁高嘅石牆 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/121627_2fa2fc01dcb5329549ec26c52570114f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F121627_2fa2fc01dcb5329549ec26c52570114f.png&h=d0b5e73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(大概示意圖, 現實石牆高啲)<br />\n<br />\n就企去後面放低包檸檬茶 <br />\n攞部電話出嚟諗住轉一轉歌<br />\n呢個時候一對準備上車嘅夫婦見到<br />\n然後指住就屌鳩我<br />\n&ldquo;啲後生仔真係冇公德心<br />\n亂咁掉啲垃圾<br />\n成個城市比佢哋搞亂晒... X&amp;:$&gt;#\\..&rdquo;<br />\n講左兩三句開門就上咗車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地上咗車入到巴士係玻璃望出嚟<br />\n仲繼續吟吟沉沉咁<br />\n我就攞返起包檸檬茶繼續飲又望鳩住佢哋<br />\n喺司機閂門之前我左佢架巴士<br />\n同司機講話等一陣<br />\n走埋去兩個廢老面前<br />\n大大聲講<br />\n大佬 我飲完就會行過垃圾桶去掉啦<br />\n況且車又未到 包野又未飲晒<br />\n擺低啲嘢轉首歌姐 <br />\n你見到我放低包野就話我亂掉垃圾<br />\n你冇撚野呀<br />\n講完佢哋O撚左咀 我頭也不回就落車了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有兩種人我真係好撚憎<br />\n一種係倚老賣老嘅廢老<br />\n另一種係以為拖住個B大晒<br />\n就恃&rdquo;細&rdquo;凌人嘅閪女人(or無賴父母)<br />\n真係唔使驚 你冇唔啱就出聲<br />\n屌鳩番佢哋<br />\n唔係老同細就可以不分對錯既都盲目尊重包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1071a422df93345fc0c1badd2026be0964429ab","tid":800643,"uid":2785,"like":243,"dislike":3,"score":240,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"好波呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f35e742c9ca58ebe9710195bed28bc0394d70fe","tid":800643,"uid":32577,"like":955,"dislike":7,"score":948,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"司機:依家啲後生仔搭車都唔俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25be2aa611471dcc8ac568138df32399367318a1","tid":800643,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6b6139c45724667d73f32f145fcfa8107eb549","tid":800643,"uid":19218,"like":459,"dislike":1,"score":458,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"呢啲行為要支持<br />\n<br />\n啲仆街下下先入為主<br />\n<br />\n標籤哂所有後生仔"},{"pid":"8ff393a9817de915c7274b683c86425870032909","tid":800643,"uid":53361,"like":8,"dislike":99,"score":-91,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:30:41.000Z","msg":"屌得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbetween 勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e7221aeaeec0e5ff33bc8681acab3ffd10ca7a","tid":800643,"uid":179108,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"樓主靚波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b2d36863176e10f80f9ee2b28d684d86189e4b","tid":800643,"uid":6959,"like":229,"dislike":2,"score":227,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e9cfea3a3436906ff1781029338dd63bf18a0e6","tid":800643,"uid":43117,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"型棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853033f9d12b3963f0788b2950b2e46851507bee","tid":800643,"uid":34223,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"樓pig ho ball <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7526166415b1d25acea40de6af4eb1f559495b91","tid":800643,"uid":52087,"like":77,"dislike"