eplyTime":"2018-08-31T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"其實無人睇到,佢包檸檬茶就唔會攞返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"講真大部份巴士站隔離都有個垃圾桶<br />\n除非係大陸人先會亂掉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5747d89d65d9be694c982e253d3dd430088947","tid":800643,"uid":131686,"like":250,"dislike":6,"score":244,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"樓豬應該揸住包檸檬茶，一路追巴士一路講<br />\n「我屌爆你個西啊，我屌穿你個西啊」"},{"pid":"c2d3e6b1c9b0ca7336d3b4a73ae468c24c9c6790","tid":800643,"uid":1880,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T17:59:43.000Z","msg":"你上車講等陣之後個司機竟然冇關門開車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfb67b21773ff6008fe303f2c98b5f6c2b423cd","tid":800643,"uid":36152,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T18:15:54.000Z","msg":"屌得好，<br />\n廢老經常唔知頭唔知路走去屌"},{"pid":"70540f8d77591b3da314677d86e8f682b2e7b03c","tid":800643,"uid":68457,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T23:20:50.000Z","msg":"我以為樓主心口真係幅相入面嘅石牆咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b979e9175da982ff57ac47205d5fec19435e85","tid":800643,"uid":78304,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T23:29:21.000Z","msg":"做得好, 佢受氣好過你受氣"},{"pid":"6f551f1920b332fb26fed2691746e8e59beea1e3","tid":800643,"uid":60744,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T23:50:05.000Z","msg":"之前我係尖沙咀睇緊㗎車邊度排隊，啲人又排到睇唔撚到條隊，我行前望下邊邊先係我搭果㗎車隊尾，屌有條八婆廢中又係係度屌9我唔好插隊，話排隊啦咁<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線，我話我睇緊條隊排咩車，佢仲話我瓜田李下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次駛唔駛係額頭寫自己搭咩車畀人睇"},{"pid":"bae2cf067dee4039887af6910accd9d55e3b0f99","tid":800643,"uid":57410,"like":9,"dislike":84,"score":-75,"citedBy":2,"rep