 />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"畀 cctvb ,  同 啲奶狗共報 洗腦洗得多"},{"pid":"161fc4cf154af13808b8e28cc49dcc878bd44879","tid":800643,"uid":200145,"like":8,"dislike":20,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說琴日等巴士翻屋企<br />\n左手攞住一袋野 右手攞住包檸檬茶<br />\n戴住耳機一路聽歌一路行一路走<br />\n去到巴士站 見後面有大概心口咁高嘅石牆 <br />\n<br />\n就企去後面放低包檸檬茶 <br />\n攞部電話出嚟諗住轉一轉歌<br />\n呢個時候一對準備上車嘅夫婦見到<br />\n然後指住就屌鳩我<br />\n&ldquo;啲後生仔真係冇公德心<br />\n亂咁掉啲垃圾<br />\n成個城市比佢哋搞亂晒... X&amp;:$&gt;#\\..&rdquo;<br />\n講左兩三句開門就上咗車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地上咗車入到巴士係玻璃望出嚟<br />\n仲繼續吟吟沉沉咁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我就攞返起包檸檬茶繼續飲又望鳩住佢哋<br />\n喺司機閂門之前我左佢架巴士<br />\n同司機講話等一陣<br />\n走埋去兩個廢老面前<br />\n大大聲講<br />\n大佬 我飲完就會行過垃圾桶去掉啦<br />\n況且車又未到 包野又未飲晒<br />\n擺低啲嘢轉首歌姐 <br />\n你見到我放低包野就話我亂掉垃圾<br />\n你冇撚野呀<br />\n講完佢哋O撚左咀 我頭也不回就落車了</span><br />\n<br />\n紅字為樓主幻想"},{"pid":"d4ac15bf2a865e5817b88548bd687a7d3d4a3b96","tid":800643,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"由道德高地瞬間跌落谷底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67619c32da8b5809a007dd2f9b81dbd9b437e76c","tid":800643,"uid":150163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274809aa4a352cdf4c930ec75c5d18d2ff39f5e3","tid":800643,"uid":11753,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:03:40.000Z","msg":"香港上一代其實係咪心理變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚鍾意揾嘢屌後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大陸屄搞到香港污煙瘴氣又唔見班柒頭出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"根本上一代鍾意屌下一代係必然嘅定律<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c389642a55bffe6a95f01299f9adb7f0ed58746b","tid":800643,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c72ad22a51b63e1ba8990807e2e96ac43c5b4c","tid":800643,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22b7de128672e2ec5fb857003e14d417bfcba46","tid":800643,"uid":1587,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"我返屋企有次禁完制等lift<br />\n咁就玩下手機先啦<br />\n<br />\n咁部lift到左地下，但熄左個制盞燈，但可能過多十零秒先開門<br />\n<br />\n咁岩有個師奶入黎，見到部lift係G樓，燈制無著，就話：掛住玩手機又唔禁制<br />\n<br />\n我真係火都黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻大大聲聲話：我禁左制喇，部lift黎到個制緊係熄左啦"},{"pid":"b9ea205eb22ee900fa8a374c897e6e52bbf6e10c","tid":800643,"uid":32615,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:39:43.000Z","msg":"試過搭小巴有個八婆睇位睇到行去車尾睇<br />\n咁以為佢走撚咗就上車即刻比佢屌我打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11715401bdd450a5f0d85e4cdd2835d26ecfa65b","tid":800643,"uid":64155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"好耶!<br />\n屌柒啲廢老臭閪 good <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab618bd8f231121aa0794990a925a0f388f7f7be","tid":800643,"uid":85117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"直覺話比我聽，屌人個段係現實中係無發生到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0113f616e737818c3379848945c623ef485a67a0","tid":800643,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"ching good ball!"},{"pid":"002d8eb6ba3370ece9f3f8654870ede5b3f9f445","tid":800643,"uid":3167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"冇追巴士屌穿佢個閪？"},{"pid":"a14d5dfc75792698c25eef9a531a42eb74417222","tid":800643,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:15:17.000Z","msg":"如果下下都要咁樣屌<br />\n日日都唔知要周圍屌幾多次<br />\n總有班廢中廢老乜都唔知就加把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b638a3d41260e7be7e915548007b1456a3a44079","tid":800643,"uid":153401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:15:34.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be296c3d7122d2ef9feac81fb98c97542d70d164","tid":800643,"uid":85659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:17:32.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"fe39c1dc02ea03658777a69ec8b54dcc6db14c5c","tid":800643,"uid":96756,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:21:08.000Z","msg":"兒登仔咪又係單憑自己見到既野不問因由就屌左先<br />\n<br />\n所以巴士果2老都係兒登仔<br />\n無錯喎"},{"pid":"8ec8915116af9fc32365455ae9298a093a0af908","tid":800643,"uid":104218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"支持香港人口大清洗<br />\n50歲以上全部消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b56309f897dc80024666b55d618a4d9eafd1e4","tid":800643,"uid":193361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"樓主，做得好，有錯要認，無錯一定唔可以硬食"},{"pid":"ce7f96297b9d014543ed965e6a2c8d60e43568a0","tid":800643,"uid":65887,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:28:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ufFa9CpOtiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DufFa9CpOtiU&d=2w%2Bf58oZeIvkdAHGcO9PK5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ae0035ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ufFa9CpOtiU</a>"},{"pid":"7deec23663521c983c2db9ad0872fece44b58bad","tid":800643,"uid":131339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"91720d1b899a0a4207340d7f2d76515f56b6945d","tid":800643,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T04:48:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說琴日等巴士翻屋企<br />\n左手攞住一袋野 右手攞住包檸檬茶<br />\n戴住耳機一路聽歌一路行一路走<br />\n去到巴士站 見後面有大概心口咁高嘅石牆 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/121627_2fa2fc01dcb5329549ec26c52570114f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F121627_2fa2fc01dcb5329549ec26c52570114f.png&h=d0b5e73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(大概示意圖, 現實石牆高啲)<br />\n<br />\n就企去後面放低包檸檬茶 <br />\n攞部電話出嚟諗住轉一轉歌<br />\n呢個時候一對準備上車嘅夫婦見到<br />\n然後指住就屌鳩我<br />\n&ldquo;啲後生仔真係冇公德心<br />\n亂咁掉啲垃圾<br />\n成個城市比佢哋搞亂晒... X&amp;:$&gt;#\\..&rdquo;<br />\n講左兩三句開門就上咗車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地上咗車入到巴士係玻璃望出嚟<br />\n仲繼續吟吟沉沉咁<br />\n我就攞返起包檸檬茶繼續飲又望鳩住佢哋<br />\n喺司機閂門之前我左佢架巴士<br />\n同司機講話等一陣<br />\n走埋去兩個廢老面前<br />\n大大聲講<br />\n大佬 我飲完就會行過垃圾桶去掉啦<br />\n況且車又未到 包野又未飲晒<br />\n擺低啲嘢轉首歌姐 <br />\n你見到我放低包野就話我亂掉垃圾<br />\n你冇撚野呀<br />\n講完佢哋O撚左咀 我頭也不回就落車了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有兩種人我真係好撚憎<br />\n一種係倚老賣老嘅廢老<br />\n另一種係以為拖住個B大晒<br />\n就恃&rdquo;細&rdquo;凌人嘅閪女人(or無賴父母)<br />\n真係唔使驚 你冇唔啱就出聲<br />\n屌鳩番佢哋<br />\n唔係老同細就可以不分對錯既都盲目尊重包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"屌得好呀,  如果見到d 直路行喺人前面食煙同埋 拎遮 打橫拎 遮頭同尾篤住人果d撚樣 , 幫幫手 教訓下佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c6bda98b0ac6fb2182247d66ef1f8563424637","tid":800643,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"需而係創意台，不過正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bc82b7f47a58b35b5a1fb5e294ab296cc04b8d","tid":800643,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a5747d89d65d9be694c982e253d3dd430088947","tid":800643,"uid":131686,"like":250,"dislike":6,"score":244,"citedBy":3,"rep